  "detailed_description": "<h1>♥</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/36b33c0a6d916da217ac76ed1c118ada.avif?t=1774245610\" width=1560 height=289 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/e69c99970a9c6da624dfff3559c25246.poster.avif?t=1774245610\" width=1170 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/e69c99970a9c6da624dfff3559c25246.webm?t=1774245610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/e69c99970a9c6da624dfff3559c25246.mp4?t=1774245610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pick a song from your PC. Your cute little friends will start playing right away!</strong>⚡</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Auto-generated charts</strong>: Add any song and difficulties from easy to hard are generated automatically!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play however you want</strong>: Press any key you like. There's no right or wrong way to play!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your style, your sound</strong>: Each of the 5 friends has their own unique sound. Which keys to press is entirely up to you!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Auto Play included</strong>: Let your friends take the wheel and perform on their own!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Built-in songs</strong>: 60+ hand-picked songs that fit the vibe, included right out of the box!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customization</strong>: Swap out character outfits and PERFECT effects to match your style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Workshop support</strong>: Use custom skins from the Workshop to change characters and button sounds!🌈</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/b2a8d8e952bfa6932d2e9648d2ac8a69.poster.avif?t=1774245610\" width=1170 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/b2a8d8e952bfa6932d2e9648d2ac8a69.webm?t=1774245610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/b2a8d8e952bfa6932d2e9648d2ac8a69.mp4?t=1774245610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pick the vibe — Upbeat, Chill, Cute, or Intense! 🎧</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each song comes with its own cover art featuring the adorable WINE characters. Find the perfect track for your mood!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/e07a81e665c5b60301c6a52d870488cd.poster.avif?t=1774245610\" width=1170 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/e07a81e665c5b60301c6a52d870488cd.webm?t=1774245610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/e07a81e665c5b60301c6a52d870488cd.mp4?t=1774245610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your song can be anywhere — just find it in the browser and you're good to go!</strong>🗂️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No complicated setup. Just pick a song and multiple difficulties are ready to play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/2c861964784524d30aeb3d1514b59a75.poster.avif?t=1774245610\" width=1170 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/2c861964784524d30aeb3d1514b59a75.webm?t=1774245610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/2c861964784524d30aeb3d1514b59a75.mp4?t=1774245610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Press a key and your friends go 'boing!' — play it your way! 🎀</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You don't have to be perfect. Just press whatever feels right!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>More features!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports a wide range of resolutions from <strong>4:3</strong> to <strong>21:9</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remap each character to any key you want. Set it up your way!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the in-game browser to navigate to any folder, or just type the path directly!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's also a mode where no notes appear — just play freely to the music!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built-in BPM metronome! If you don't know your song's BPM, you can set it manually.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's a score, but no game over. Chill out or go for ALL PERFECT — up to you!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hit multiple keys on a single note? Totally fine. Play the same song a different way every time!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements are in too! Keep an eye out for the hidden weird ones.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/e69c99970a9c6da624dfff3559c25246.poster.avif?t=1774245610\" width=1170 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/e69c99970a9c6da624dfff3559c25246.webm?t=1774245610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/e69c99970a9c6da624dfff3559c25246.mp4?t=1774245610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pick a song from your PC. Your cute little friends will start playing right away!</strong>⚡</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Auto-generated charts</strong>: Add any song and difficulties from easy to hard are generated automatically!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play however you want</strong>: Press any key you like. There's no right or wrong way to play!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your style, your sound</strong>: Each of the 5 friends has their own unique sound. Which keys to press is entirely up to you!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Auto Play included</strong>: Let your friends take the wheel and perform on their own!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Built-in songs</strong>: 60+ hand-picked songs that fit the vibe, included right out of the box!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customization</strong>: Swap out character outfits and PERFECT effects to match your style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Workshop support</strong>: Use custom skins from the Workshop to change characters and button sounds!🌈</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop play