" width=1170 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/2c861964784524d30aeb3d1514b59a75.webm?t=1774245610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4258870/extras/2c861964784524d30aeb3d1514b59a75.mp4?t=1774245610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Press a key and your friends go 'boing!' — play it your way! 🎀</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You don't have to be perfect. Just press whatever feels right!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>More features!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports a wide range of resolutions from <strong>4:3</strong> to <strong>21:9</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remap each character to any key you want. Set it up your way!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the in-game browser to navigate to any folder, or just type the path directly!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's also a mode where no notes appear — just play freely to the music!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built-in BPM metronome! If you don't know your song's BPM, you can set it manually.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's a score, but no game over. Chill out or go for ALL PERFECT — up to you!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hit multiple keys on a single note? Totally fine. Play the same song a different way every time!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements are in too! Keep an eye out for the hidden weird ones.</p></li></ul>",
